    "title": "SEO Strategy",
    "text": "Most people think SEO is too technical\n\nIt only feels that way because no one explains it simply\n\nSo I broke everything down step-by-step in this carousel\nIf you follow these steps, you‚Äôll build an SEO strategy that actually works\n\nHere‚Äôs the quick version üëá\n\n1. Know your goal\nTraffic, leads or visibility?\nClear goals guide your whole strategy\n\n2. Understand your audience\nWhat do they search?\nWhat problems are they trying to solve?\n\n3. Pick the right keywords\nSkip the tough ones\nStart with low-competition terms that match real intent.\n\n4. Create helpful content\nPractical, honest, and easy to read.\nNot keyword-stuffed\n\n5. Fix your website basics\nClean URLs, good titles, fast loading, mobile-friendly.\nSmall changes, big results\n\n6. Build trust with backlinks\nGuest posts, expert quotes, and social visibility.\nQuality matters more than volume\n\n7. Track and improve\nLook at the data\nUpdate what's not working.\nGrow slowly but consistently\n\nAll the detailed breakdowns are in the carousel\nSave it for later if you want a simple SEO roadmap\n\nIf you found this useful drop a comment share it with someone who needs it\nfollow for more simple SEO breakdowns\n\n#SEO #DigitalMarketing #ContentStrategy #SEOTips #GoogleSearch #MarketingTips #UAEbusiness",
