    "text": "Google Just Changed the Rules of SEO\n\nYou‚Äôre posting consistently.\nYour content looks great.\nYet Google ignores you.\n\nHere‚Äôs why.\n\nGoogle‚Äôs AI Overviews now decide what appears first.\n\nThey no longer reward surface-level content.\n\nThey prioritise depth, originality, and real human experience.\n\nIf your content only repeats what others say it disappears.\n\nWhat works now:\n\n‚úî Share what you‚Äôve learned from real clients or projects\n\n‚úî Add your own insights, not recycled points\n\n‚úî Explain why something works, not just what to do\n\n‚úî Keep your tone natural and human\n Google can detect effort and trust\n\nAI isn‚Äôt your enemy. Generic content is.\n\nStart building posts that reflect what you actually know.\nShow the process, the mistakes, the lessons.\n\nBecause the future of SEO belongs to voices that sound real.\n\nStart today rewrite one page or post with your real experience and see how your visibility changes.",
