    "text": "What is SEO, and how do on-page SEO, off-page SEO, technical SEO, and local SEO work to improve your website's visibility in search results?\n\nSEO enhances your website's visibility in search results. You attract more visitors from search engines like Google through relevant content and performance.\n\nOn-page SEO\n\nOptimize titles, headers, and content for keywords\n\nAdd internal links for better navigation\n\nImprove image alt text for relevance\n\nOff-page SEO\n\nBuild credible backlinks from trusted sites\n\nEngage in guest blogging and digital PR\n\nGain mentions and links through social profiles\n\nTechnical SEO\n\nImprove website speed and loading performance\n\nFix broken links and crawl errors\n\nUse XML sitemaps for indexing\n\nLocal SEO\n\nAdd your business to Google Business Profile\n\nInclude local keywords and address in content\n\nGet reviews from nearby customers",
