    "text": "‚Äãü§ñ Answer Engine Optimization (AEO)\n‚ÄãAEO stands for Answer Engine Optimization, and it is the evolution of traditional Search Engine Optimization (SEO) designed for the age of AI, voice assistants, and instant-answer snippets. The goal of AEO is not just to get your website to rank high on a results page, but to ensure your content is chosen by platforms (like Google's AI Overviews, Siri, Alexa, or even ChatGPT) as the direct, featured answer to a user's question üéØ. This requires crafting content that is incredibly clear, concise, and structured (often using FAQs or bullet points) so that the AI can easily scrape, understand, and confidently present your information as the definitive, trustworthy response. It's about securing \"Position Zero,\" where you become the knowledge, not just the link. If SEO is getting the customer to knock on your door, AEO is having your answer appear right on their screen before they even have to click. #trading #digitalmarketing #digitalmarketing",
