    "authorProfileUrl": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mansi-kumari-410177383?miniProfileUrn=urn%3Ali%3Afs_miniProfile%3AACoAAF6H5IwB9kono75rkgP6vJopOKghCNURTJo"
