    "text": "üöÄ SEO vs AEO: The Must-Know Shift in Digital Strategy\n\nSearch Engine Optimization (SEO) and Answer Engine Optimization (AEO) are reshaping how brands appear online. üåê\n\nAs search evolves from keywords to conversational AI, understanding this shift isn‚Äôt optional ‚Äî it‚Äôs essential for long-term visibility.\n\nüëâ Dive into our new guide breaking down:\n\n-The key differences between SEO and AEO\n-Real-world examples of how AEO impacts your brand\n-Actionable insights to future-proof your digital presence\n-FAQs every marketer should know\n\nüìñ Read the full guide here: https://lnkd.in/eZJ6aykg\n#AISEO #AEO #DigitalMarketing #AIsearch #SEOtips #SkySEODigital #MiamiMarketing",
