    "text": "SEO vs GEO vs AEO: Decision Matrix\n\nùêÜùêûùê≠ ùêìùê°ùêû ùêñùêûùêûùê§ùê•ùê≤ ùêÄùêà ùêÅùê´ùê¢ùêûùêüùê¢ùêßùê†, ùê≠ùê°ùêû ùê©ùê´ùêûùê¶ùê¢ùêÆùê¶ ùêßùêûùê∞ùê¨ùê•ùêûùê≠ùê≠ùêûùê´ ùê¨ùê¶ùêöùê´ùê≠ ùê•ùêûùêöùêùùêûùê´ùê¨ ùê´ùêûùêöùêù. ùêíùêÆùêõùê¨ùêúùê´ùê¢ùêõùêû ùêßùê®ùê∞ ‚Üí aiforleaders.com\n\nOriginal post:\n__________\n\nSEO vs AEO vs GEO - What should you focus on?\n\nHere's a simple framework my clients use:\n\n‚Üí SEO = Rank in Google\n‚Üí AEO = Be the direct answer\n‚Üí GEO = Be cited by AI \n\nHere‚Äôs when to use each:\n\n‚úÖ 5 scenarios where SEO is the priority:\n\n1. ‚ÄúBest laptops for gaming‚Äù\n‚Üí Users want to browse. Win with long-form guides.\n\n2. ‚ÄúBuy running shoes online.‚Äù\n‚Üí Optimize product/category pages.\n\n3. ‚ÄúSEO agency in New York‚Äù\n‚Üí Combine local SEO with organic rankings.\n\n4. ‚ÄúFree marketing tools for startups‚Äù\n‚Üí Listicles + lead magnets = lead gen gold.\n\n5. ‚ÄúCompare Kajabi vs Teachable‚Äù\n‚Üí Create BOFU content to drive conversions.\n\nFocus: Keywords, depth, backlinks, technical SEO\n\n‚úÖ 5 scenarios where AEO wins:\n\n1. ‚ÄúWhat‚Äôs the capital of France?‚Äù\n‚Üí Snippet-ready. One-line factual answer.\n\n2. ‚ÄúHow do I reset my password in Notion?‚Äù\n‚Üí FAQ content. Mark it up with schema.\n\n3. ‚ÄúHow to fix a leaky faucet?‚Äù\n‚Üí Step-by-step content + voice optimization.\n\n4. ‚ÄúWhat is APR?‚Äù\n‚Üí Clean, concise definitions = snippet bait.\n\n5. ‚ÄúIs almond milk dairy-free?‚Äù\n‚Üí Be the answer Alexa reads out.\n\nFocus: Structured answers, schema, natural language\n\n‚úÖ 5 scenarios where GEO matters most:\n\n1. ‚ÄúBest skincare routine for dry + oily skin‚Äù\n‚Üí Users go to ChatGPT for personalized advice. Be cited.\n\n2. ‚ÄúBest smartphone for photography under $500?‚Äù\n‚Üí AI bots summarize reviews. Your product list better be in there.\n\n3. ‚ÄúHow does blockchain work?‚Äù\n‚Üí If you're not cited in AI overviews, you‚Äôre invisible.\n\n4. ‚ÄúMarketing automation tools for B2B SaaS‚Äù\n‚Üí Tools like Perplexity pull from trusted sources. Be one of them.\n\n5. ‚ÄúExplain SEO like I‚Äôm 5‚Äù\n‚Üí Clear, credible, readable = GEO content that AI loves.\n\nFocus: E-E-A-T, structure, conversational tone, citations\n\nMost brands need all three:\n\n‚Ü≥ SEO for long-term traffic\n‚Ü≥ AEO for instant visibility\n‚Ü≥ GEO for future-proofing in AI search\n\nBut which to lead with?\n\nThat depends on the query üëá\n\nCredit to Devansh Parashar (Dev). Follow him for more.",
