    "text": "Save this: the SEO playbook I use to drive compounding growth\n\n- Map intent, not just keywords: cluster topics, ship a pillar + supporting pages, and own a niche\n- Win the click: benefit-first titles, compelling meta, and a 2‚Äì3 sentence intro that answers the query fast\n- Show E‚ÄëE‚ÄëA‚ÄëT: real author bios, citations, last‚Äëupdated dates, and original images/data\n- Fix the tech: pass Core Web Vitals, kill 404s/redirect chains, canonicalize variants, clean faceted URLs, keep sitemaps lean\n- Build relevance with internal links: add 3‚Äì5 links to and from every new page using descriptive anchors\n- Refresh > more content: update, consolidate, and prune; add info‚Äëgain sections (FAQs, comparisons, pricing, pros/cons)\n- Earn links that last: digital PR, unique data assets, partner pages, community mentions‚Äîskip spam\n- Measure what matters: non‚Äëbrand organic conversions, assisted revenue, GSC query trends ‚Üí roadmap\n\nSimple systems > secret hacks. Which one are you shipping this week? Comment ‚Äúplaybook‚Äù and I‚Äôll share my templates. #sultanofSEO",
