    "text": "üöÄ SEO Tip of the Day ‚Äî Rank Faster in 2025\n\nIf you want your website to rank higher, focus on search intent, not just keywords.\n\nüîç What is Search Intent?\nIt means understanding what exactly the user wants when they search on Google.\n\nüí° Types of Search Intent:\n\nInformational: ‚ÄúHow to build backlinks‚Äù\n\nNavigational: ‚ÄúFacebook login‚Äù\n\nCommercial: ‚ÄúBest SEO tools‚Äù\n\nTransactional: ‚ÄúBuy guest posts‚Äù\n\n\nüéØ Why It Matters?\n\nGoogle ranks the content only when it matches the user's actual intention.\n\nüî• Quick Tip:\n\nBefore writing any article, ask:\nüëâ ‚ÄúUser kya dhoond raha hai?‚Äù\nMatch your content with that ‚Äî your rankings will naturally improve.",
