    "title": "",
    "text": "Traditional SEO is slowly dying. \n\nAnd most businesses are ignoring it...\n\nEven though it's the most significant shift we've seen in decades. \n\nWith over 800 million people using ChatGPT weekly,¬†\nAnd 77% of searches now ending with AI answers...\n\nAI Search is becoming the new normal. \n\nIf you're still optimising for traditional SEO alone,¬†\nYour business will be invisible to millions of potential customers.\n\nHere's how things are changing: \n\nSEO was built on ranking keywords, while AI search works on context.\n\nTo be discovered now, your brand must be part of the conversation.\n\n‚ùå Old success meant ranking at the top of a results page.\n‚òëÔ∏è New success means being cited in the right conversations.\n\nThe search process itself has changed. \n\nCustomers rarely decide after one question now.\nThey ask 3 to 7 follow-up questions.\n\nThey reveal budgets, compare alternatives, and narrow down options.\n\nEach prompt in a multi-step conversation with an AI platform is a \"turn.\"\n\nThink of it like a dialogue:\n\nTurn 1: \"What are the best project management tools?\" (AI responds with a list)¬†\nTurn 2: \"Which of these works best for remote teams?\" (AI narrows down options)\nTurn 3: \"What's the pricing for Asana vs Monday.com?\" (AI provides comparison)\nTurn 4: \"Which one integrates with Slack?\" (AI gives implementation details)\nTurn 5: \"How long does setup take?\" (User is now purchase-ready)\n\nSingle-turn searches have conversion rates of 1-2%.\nMulti-turn conversations have conversion rates of 15-35%.\n\n80% of decisions happen between Turn 3 and 5.¬†\nYet, most brands are invisible at those stages. \n\nIn order to thrive in AI Search, businesses must: \n\n1. Optimise For Context, Not Keywords:\n\n- Write content that answers real questions people ask AI\n- Use natural language and conversational phrasing\n- Structure content with clear headings and direct answers\n- Implement FAQ and Q&A formats\n\n2. Show Up In Multi-Turn Conversations:\n\n- Build comprehensive content¬†\n- Address budgets, comparisons, and constraints¬†\n- Include implementation details and next steps\n- Track where you appear in conversations\n\n3. Build Conversation Authority:\n\n- Get cited across multiple platforms¬†\n- Create original research and unique data¬†\n- Display author credentials and expertise clearly\n- Monitor citations in ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, and Claude\n\nThe brands that adapt now will maintain their authority...\n\nWhile their competitors are stuck chasing page one rankings.\n\nHave you started optimising for AI Search?¬†\nDrop your thoughts in the comments.\n\nFor the easiest possible way to implement these steps...\nGet started with Searchable. \n\nIt's an autonomous SEO & AEO Growth Engineer that\nAnalyses, fixes, and scales your website automatically to drive customers.\n\nLearn more here:\nhttps://lnkd.in/gTfCj6Ht\n\n‚ôªÔ∏è Repost to share this framework with your network.¬†\nFollow Searchable for more on SEO/AEO/GEO.",
